description: This header file defines internal function prototypes for the TLS Cipher Switch Object within the Transport Layer Security implementation. It includes function declarations for receiving and sending TLS messages, as well as handling ChangeCipherSpec messages, which are part of the TLS protocol process.

methods.name: TlsCsoRecv
methods.description: Handles the reception of data for the TLS Cipher Switch Object.

methods.name: TlsCsoSend
methods.description: Handles the transmission of data for the TLS Cipher Switch Object.
